"{\"uid\": \"rte.ie-kids-2024-0728-1462249-monkstowns-olympic-boxer-jack-marley-is-living-the-dream\", \"text\": \"  Team Ireland's boxers are fighting for gold at the Paris Olympic Games, and Monkstown Boxing Club's Jack Marley is back in the ring this evening.  RT\\u00c9jr caught up with Jack for some hard-hitting questions!! Press play to see his Quick Q&A where he tells us he is living the dream. And he reveals his first ever concert...  Get Paris 2024updates from RT\\u00c9 Sportand tune in to RT\\u00c92 and RT\\u00c9 Player.  FollowRT\\u00c9jr on InstaandTikTokfor more fun social clips with Team Ireland athletes!    And, when you are tuning in to RT\\u00c9's boxing coverage, you might hear some new words and phrases. So, we asked Jack tells us whats what in the ring.  Watch the 2024 Olympic Games with 14 hours of televised action on RT\\u00c92 and RT\\u00c9 Player each day.  Listen to extensive radio coverage on RT\\u00c9 Radio 1 and 2fm's Game On and follow each moment from Paris on RT\\u00c9.ie, the RT\\u00c9 News app and all RT\\u00c9 digital platforms. Listen to the daily RT\\u00c9 Sport Olympics Podcast.      \\u00a9 RT\\u00c9 2026. RT\\u00c9.ie is the website of Raidi\\u00f3 Teilif\\u00eds \\u00c9ireann, Ireland's National Public Service Media. RT\\u00c9 is not responsible for the content of external internet sites.  Images Courtesy of Getty Images.\"}"